[
  "Franco Bittar Garcia is the grandson of Luiza Trajano Donato and Pelegrino José Donato, who founded retailer Magazine Luiza in 1957.",
  "Bittar Garcia serves as a board member of Magazine Luiza, whose CEO is his cousin Frederico Trajano.",
  "Nicknamed \"the Amazon of Brazil,\" Magazine Luiza's e-commerce platforms bring in 40% of the company's total revenues.",
  "Bittar Garcia lives in the city of Franca, in the state of São Paulo, where Magazine Luiza was founded."
]